Package: libocsqlite1
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: SQLite helper library for OLLMchat
 OLLMchat is a library and embeddable widget that provides LLM access
 and tool integration for applications.
 .
 This package contains libocsqlite.so.

