         libocmarkdowngtk1 (= ${binary:Version}),
         libollamaweb1 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: OLLMchat - LLM chat application
 OLLMchat is a library and embeddable widget that provides LLM access
 and tool integration for applications.
 .
 This package contains the main ollmchat application.

Package: ollmchat-tools
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends},
         ${misc:Depends},
         libocmarkdown1 (= ${binary:Version})
Description: Command-line tools for OLLMchat
 OLLMchat is a library and embeddable widget that provides LLM access
 and tool integration for applications.
 .
 This package contains command-line tools:
  - oc-md2html: Markdown to HTML converter
  - oc-html2md: HTML to Markdown converter

Package: ollmchat-doc
Architecture: all
