Description: Test executables and documentation for OLLMchat
 OLLMchat is a library and embeddable widget that provides LLM access
 and tool integration for applications.
 .
 This package contains test executables and documentation:
  - ollmchat-cli: Command-line LLM chat and agent-tool executable
  - oc-markdown-test: Markdown parser test executable
